nverted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><b>NFTxCards Adult Metaverse<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/b><\/h4>\n<p>The Crypto Muses of Protest NFT collection kicks off the project\u2019s development of an 18+ metaverse, which\u2019ll serve as a virtual playground for all things kink. The <strong>explicit metaverse will feature an array of different activities<\/strong> which free you from any limitations, including the release of exclusive videos from real models, as well as an official NFT marketplace (which<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span>every Crypto Muse holder will have initial access to).<\/p>\n<p>The metaverse will also incorporate the project\u2019s <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/dolls.nftxcards.com\/\">NFTxDoll<\/a> arm, which launches life-like, 3D animated renderings of popular figures in the adult industry.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><b>Roadmap<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/b><\/h4>\n<p>The project will journey through its roadmap in accordance with the sales of its Crypto Muse NFTs.<\/p>\n<p>After 10% of the collection is sold, the project will begin allocating money to early investors and adopters, followed by investments into marketplace marketing when 20% is sold. Developers and designers for the adult metaverse will then be hired once 30% is sold.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>A token-gated exclusive merch store where users can buy limited edition items and gear will then launch once 40% is sold, and an \u2018X-Club Performers Studio Shoot\u2019 will take place when half of the collection is gone.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>As the project\u2019s community continues to be built in wake of 50% of it selling out, a council for making decisions on future performer selection and general marketing strategy will be elected, followed by the launch of a liquidity pool for the marketplace, as well as the hosting of parties for <strong>X-Club members and performers.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>The final stage in the project\u2019s current roadmap is the hiring of lawyers for the IPOs of the company.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><b>Team<\/b><\/h4>\n<p>The NFTxCards team consists of five individuals which make up a CEO, CTO, Project Lead, COO, and Talent Acquisition, as well as a \u2018Dream Team\u2019 collective made up of the most talented and dedicated adult industry and crypto enthusiasts.<\/p>\n<p><b>Find out more &gt;&gt; <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/nft\u0425plazas\">Website<\/a><\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>Follow NFTxCards\u00a0 &gt;&gt; <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/nf\u0425plazas_tw\">Twitter<\/a><\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/nftplazas\">Like us on Facebook<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/nftplazas\/\">Follow us on Instagram<\/a><\/p>\n<p><small><em>*All investment\/financial opinions expressed by NFT Plazas are from the personal research and experience of our site moderators and are intended as educational material only. Individuals are required to fully research any product prior to making any kind of investment.<\/em><\/small><\/p>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-wrap\" itemtype=\"http:\/\/schema.org\/Person\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"a